Package: actogrammr
Type: Package
Title: Read in Activity Data and Plot Actograms
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Robert", "Corty", email = "rcorty@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Read in activity measurements from standard file formats
  used by circadian rhythm researchers, currently only ClockLab format,
  and process and plot the data.
